{"tid":1590880,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Steam] 示威模擬器 RIOT: Civil Unrest特價25蚊咋","createTime":"2019-09-24T02:40:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T23:06:29.000Z","uid":18265,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e82267b9f8d7f59a0ab3f7694849aed24b65482f","tid":1590880,"uid":18265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:40:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/342310/RIOT_Civil_Unrest/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F342310%2FRIOT_Civil_Unrest%2F&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obnHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=20e5bdbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://store.steampowered.com/app/342310/RIOT_Civil_Unrest/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/256741400/movie_max.webm?t=1548427857\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsteamcdn-a.akamaihd.net%2Fsteam%2Fapps%2F256741400%2Fmovie_max.webm%3Ft%3D1548427857&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obnHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=e2fb84b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/256741400/movie_max.webm?t=1548427857</a><br />\n<br />\n RIOT: Civil Unrest 帶你體驗世界唔同嘅抗爭，主線包括Indignados 西班牙反緊縮運動、Arab Spring 埃及阿拉伯之春、Keratea 希臘 同 NoTAV 意大利反高速鐵路示威，一共四大抗爭同十六個示威場面，另外仲有額外示威關卡俾大家玩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/342310/ss_ba963ec41b36ee0a19a32ac7c28c4aee9fa626bf.600x338.jpg?t=1550145354\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsteamcdn-a.akamaihd.net%2Fsteam%2Fapps%2F342310%2Fss_ba963ec41b36ee0a19a32ac7c28c4aee9fa626bf.600x338.jpg%3Ft%3D1550145354&h=195ddb75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n玩家可以扮演黑警或者示威者，善用策略驅散抗爭者，或者對抗成身裝備嘅黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n激進嘅行動可能好快搞掂，但係和平啲嘅手段可以盡量減少公眾傷亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/342310/ss_6d91e9c2ac183c26fc3446da51ef8a2be9ffc79e.600x338.jpg?t=1550145354\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsteamcdn-a.akamaihd.net%2Fsteam%2Fapps%2F342310%2Fss_6d91e9c2ac183c26fc3446da51ef8a2be9ffc79e.600x338.jpg%3Ft%3D1550145354&h=12a71b49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋可以指示示威者者同記者，用群眾嘅力量勇武或者撤退等手段平息局勢，仲要掟石仔、雞尾酒、paper bomb 同媒體嘅力量發動攻勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲可以自己設計關卡，玩其他人嘅設計，同frd 對打等等"},{"pid":"345a36fc2ff065a96b8f80b3ece7b9797867339d","tid":1590880,"uid":72457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:45:20.000Z","msg":"玩咗，出tear gas再亂棍打<br />\n好快散<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d85083a28b03657fef9c082e31f08a4250f0fe0","tid":1590880,"uid":202137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:46:24.000Z","msg":"有香港DLC就買"},{"pid":"632c3e29470429bd8d697ce31a3700662c9d4d2c","tid":1590880,"uid":18265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"345a36fc2ff065a96b8f80b3ece7b9797867339d","tid":1590880,"uid":72457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:45:20.000Z","msg":"玩咗，出tear gas再亂棍打<br />\n好快散<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T08:05:53.000Z","msg":"貼近現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3ff7b5faa816922cdc3867730e439d05e183247","tid":1590880,"uid":18265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d85083a28b03657fef9c082e31f08a4250f0fe0","tid":1590880,"uid":202137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:46:24.000Z","msg":"有香港DLC就買"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T08:06:13.000Z","msg":"鸁咗先啦"},{"pid":"133b8c021ddbd1e1e0738a39fb04fd17f92f7919","tid":1590880,"uid":33495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d85083a28b03657fef9c082e31f08a4250f0fe0","tid":1590880,"uid":202137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:46:24.000Z","msg":"有香港DLC就買"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":